G. Nicholas N. Huskinson1

M, #301541

Last Edited=2 Aug 2008

G. Nicholas N. Huskinson married Pennant Elfrida Iremonger, daughter of Thomas Lascelles Isa Shandon Valiant Iremonger and Lucille D'Oyen Parks, in 1973.1

He held the office of Circuit Court Judge.1

Penelope Jane Wilson1

F, #301542

Last Edited=12 Dec 2012

Penelope Jane Wilson is the daughter of Robert Edward Arnsby Wilson.1 She married John Laurence David Aschan, son of Carl Nils Wilhelm Gunnar Aschan and Marit Victoria Guinness, on 25 June 1970. She and John Laurence David Aschan were divorced in 1978.1

From 25 June 1970, her married name became Aschan.

Dolores Maria Agatha Wilhelmine Luise Gräfin von Fürstenberg1

F, #301546

Last Edited=13 Dec 2012

Dolores Maria Agatha Wilhelmine Luise Gräfin von Fürstenberg is the daughter of Franz Egon Graf von Fürstenberg and Gloria Rubio.2,1 She married Patrick Benjamin Guinness, son of G/Capt. Thomas Loel Evelyn Bulkeley Guinness and Hon. Joan Barbara Yarde-Buller, on 22 October 1955.3

From 22 October 1955, her married name became Guinness.

Maria Alexandra Guinness1

F, #301548, b. 24 August 1956

Last Edited=1 Aug 2008

Maria Alexandra Guinness was born on 24 August 1956.1 She is the daughter of Patrick Benjamin Guinness and Dolores Maria Agatha Wilhelmine Luise Gräfin von Fürstenberg.2 She married Count Foulques de Quatrebarbes in 1979.1 She and Count Foulques de Quatrebarbes were divorced in 1990.1

Maria Alexandra Guinness usually went by her middle name of Alexandra.1 From 1979, her married name became de Quatrebarbes. She lived in 2003 at Chemin de Bouerenes 136, Epalinges, Kanton Vaud, Switzerland .1
